{"type": "article", "id": 26297, "title": "曲木家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606081310102RVoIkr7SU64hbGz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套名为“我爱瑜伽”的家具由设计师张永和其带领的建筑设计事务所<a href=\"http://www.fcjz.com/\">非常建筑</a>和<a href=\"http://qmrd-life.com/\">曲美家居</a>携手打造，目前在上海当代艺术博物馆举行的<a href=\"http://www.powerstationofart.com/cn/exhibition/detail/f2bgxA.html\">“建筑之名 非常建筑泛设计展”</a>上展出。曲木工艺为设计创造了更大的弹性，“我爱瑜伽”系列中的每一件家具都由单独一块曲木制成。不依靠其他素材，而是以一种非常自然的方式联结的方式透露着淡定和优雅的气质。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131008vpeIS8bRGTrBh92J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131008Bje4PoDYw0ard2s9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74205379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131008aMXx6Po2A78QZUC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131009pwGd8mixUjJkn2Ro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93765281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}